<a name="LinhaPesquisa">
<h1>Linhas de pesquisa</h1>
</a>
<hr class="separator">
<div class="layout-cell layout-cell-12 data-cell"><a name='LP_Introdu&ccedil;&atilde;o de t&oacute;picos de F&iacute;sica Moderna e Contempor&acirc;nea na Escola M&eacute;dia'></a><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-3 text-align-right">
<div class="layout-cell-pad-5 text-align-right">
<b>1. </b>
</div>
</div>
<div class="layout-cell layout-cell-9">
<div class="layout-cell-pad-5">Introdução de tópicos de Física Moderna e Contemporânea na Escola Média</div>
</div><a name='LP_Hist&oacute;ria da F&iacute;sica na Forma&ccedil;&atilde;o do Professor'></a><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-3 text-align-right">
<div class="layout-cell-pad-5 text-align-right">
<b>2. </b>
</div>
</div>
<div class="layout-cell layout-cell-9">
<div class="layout-cell-pad-5">História da Física na Formação do Professor</div>
</div><a name='LP_Forma&ccedil;&atilde;o de Professores'></a><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-3 text-align-right">
<div class="layout-cell-pad-5 text-align-right">
<b>3. </b>
</div>
</div>
<div class="layout-cell layout-cell-9">
<div class="layout-cell-pad-5">Formação de Professores</div>
</div><a name='LP_Metacogni&ccedil;&atilde;o'></a><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-3 text-align-right">
<div class="layout-cell-pad-5 text-align-right">
<b>4. </b>
</div>
</div>
<div class="layout-cell layout-cell-9">
<div class="layout-cell-pad-5">Metacognição</div>
</div><a name='LP_Forma&ccedil;&atilde;o de Professor Pr&aacute;tico-Reflexivo'></a><div class="layout-cell layout-cell-3 text-align-right">
<div class="layout-cell-pad-5 text-align-right">
<b>5. </b>
</div>
</div>
<div class="layout-cell layout-cell-9">
